text: Hey Jill, come here a sec.
Why don't you take a seat?
Are you okay? You're not just spamming the easiest drinks, right?
Why don't you go home today? Get some rest, I'll take it from here.
Don't you ButtBoss me, young lady.
I need you in top form for the whole team.
Get some rest, clear your mind.
I'm sending you to the bench, soldier.
Jill, why don't you take the rest of the day off?
I have reasons to believe you've been just spamming the easiest drinks over and over again.
Don't worry, I'll take it from here. Just get some rest, will you?
That's um... punishment. Yeah, let's go with that.
Let's go out for a bit.
You've been spamming easy drinks for too long.
Come on. Come here. Gil will take care of the fort while we hang out.
I was... and I came back because you've been slacking off!
Yes! You've been serving easy drinks one after the other, haven't you? Wrong drinks at that.
I just know. Just like I know you should take a rest.
Don't you think taunting me for serving "easy drinks" of all things is too much?
Then go get some rest or I shall taunt you a second time.
You can't just go serving easy drinks that aren't even the right ones are even trying?
Just go home, you're grounded for today, young lady.
